Best_Sellers.title: Classic Belt - Cognac
Best_Sellers.desc: Perfectly styled for any occasion. A classic whether worn with denim, cords or chinos. This belt will only get better with age. The edges are dyed, burnished, waxed and each one is stamped with our signature makers mark.

Best_Sellers.title: Standard Mug
Best_Sellers.desc: Whether you’re greeting your day over coffee or mixing a hot toddy to welcome the evening, the Standard Mug brings the rich feel of hand-crafted ceramics to your table. The handle and body are slip cast together to provide a solid yet comfortable grip. The tapered, unglazed foot allows sets to nest together neatly on open shelving or counter tops.Mazama ceramics are handmade and some variation is to be expected. Mazama ceramics can be washed safely in the dishwasher, however, we recommend hand washing for the longest lifespan. For further information about how to care for your ceramics, please see our ceramic care page.

Best_Sellers.title: Journeyman - Natural
Best_Sellers.desc: The Journeyman is a perfect example of how a great concept can spring from our collaborative nature as a company. Born from an idea proposed by our retail staff, this slim-yet-sturdy wallet was subsequently designed, developed and sampled by our design-minded craftspeople on the workshop floor.Cut from 3.5oz Natural tooling leather, the Journeyman features four card slots and one central pocket for you to stash your cash - a configuration those who prefer to carry their wallet in their front pocket would appreciate.

Best_Sellers.title: Journeyman - Natural
Best_Sellers.desc: The Standard Belt emphasizes utilitarian styling and is built to last and improve with age. Featuring a matching leather keep and metal hardware, the edges are dyed, burnished, waxed, and each belt is stamped with our signature makers mark.

mazma.title: Stacking Bowl
mazma.desc: Our Stacking Bowl takes cues from Mazama’s origins; the iconic beveled base, the timeless, angular lines and the specially formulated clay. Designed to stack beautifully and efficiently, these bowls are equally at home on display in open shelving or neatly organized into cupboards. Each bowl is slip cast and hand finished so natural variation is to be expected

mazma.title: Carafe
mazma.desc: Hand blown from durable soda-lime glass, our Carafe is a versatile serving vessel for any occasion. Featuring a wide mouth opening, it’s also perfect for adding ice into a lemonade or mixed drink and easy to stir with a spoon if you wish. Topped off with a beautiful natural oak wood ball stopper, our Carafe is practical as well as beautiful.

mazma.title: Spirit Bottle
mazma.desc: Our hand blown serving bottle is sure to please even the most discerning whisky drinker. Not into spirits? This versatile vessel works great for water service too, or remove the cork and you have a stunner of a handcrafted vase.

mazma.title: Wine Glass
mazma.desc: We know the importance of taking some time to enjoy the little things in life, especially now. Why not do it with a beverage in hand?  Made from durable soda-lime glass, our wine glasses are designed and handblown in Portland, Oregon.

mazma.title: Standard Pint Glass
mazma.desc: We know the importance of taking some time to enjoy the little things in life, especially now. Why not do it with a beverage in hand?  Made from durable soda-lime glass, our wine glasses are designed and handblown in Portland, Oregon
